{"image_id": "CHD_2011_page_104", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "CHURCH & DWIGHT CO., INC. AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [383.3, 158.9, 891.8, 179.7]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [298.1, 196.4, 977.0, 217.2]}, {"text": "19. Segments", "bbox": [162.5, 246.4, 278.2, 267.2]}, {"text": "Segment Information", "bbox": [183.3, 285.5, 368.1, 306.3]}, {"text": "The Company operates three reportable segments: Consumer Domestic, Consumer International and", "bbox": [204.2, 324.7, 1042.8, 345.6]}, {"text": "Specialty Products Division (“SPD”). These segments are determined based on differences in the nature of", "bbox": [162.5, 349.7, 1053.3, 370.6]}, {"text": "products and organizational and ownership structures. The Company also has a Corporate segment.", "bbox": [162.5, 374.7, 992.2, 395.6]}, {"text": "Segment revenues are derived from the sale of the following products:", "bbox": [204.2, 428.0, 791.8, 448.8]}, {"text": "Segment", "bbox": [245.8, 475.9, 306.9, 492.5]}, {"text": "Products", "bbox": [474.8, 475.9, 538.7, 492.5]}, {"text": "Consumer Domestic", "bbox": [245.8, 504.1, 416.6, 524.9]}, {"text": "Household and personal care products", "bbox": [474.8, 504.1, 793.3, 524.9]}, {"text": "Consumer International", "bbox": [245.8, 541.1, 443.2, 561.9]}, {"text": "Primarily personal care products", "bbox": [474.8, 541.1, 746.6, 561.9]}, {"text": "SPD", "bbox": [245.8, 578.1, 284.0, 598.9]}, {"text": "Specialty chemical products", "bbox": [474.8, 578.1, 710.1, 598.9]}, {"text": "The Corporate segment income consists of equity in earnings of affiliates. The Company had 50%", "bbox": [204.2, 631.3, 1024.2, 652.1]}, {"text": "ownership interests in Armand and ArmaKleen as of December 31, 2011. The Company’s equity in earnings of", "bbox": [162.5, 656.3, 1092.9, 677.1]}, {"text": "Armand and ArmaKleen for the twelve months ended December 31, 2011, 2010 and 2009 is included in the", "bbox": [162.5, 681.3, 1063.2, 702.1]}, {"text": "Corporate segment. On September 22, 2011, the Company formed an operating joint venture, Natronx, in which", "bbox": [162.5, 706.3, 1098.7, 727.1]}, {"text": "it has a one-third ownership interest. The Company’s equity in Natronx’s net loss for the period ended", "bbox": [162.5, 731.3, 1016.2, 752.1]}, {"text": "December 31, 2011 is also included in the Corporate segment.", "bbox": [162.5, 756.3, 682.2, 777.1]}, {"text": "Some of the subsidiaries that are included in the Consumer International segment manufacture and sell", "bbox": [204.2, 809.5, 1062.2, 830.4]}, {"text": "personal care products to the Consumer Domestic segment. These sales are eliminated from the Consumer", "bbox": [162.5, 834.5, 1051.1, 855.4]}, {"text": "International segment results set forth in the table below.", "bbox": [162.5, 859.5, 637.5, 880.4]}, {"text": "The following table presents selected financial information relating to the Company’s segments for each of", "bbox": [204.2, 912.7, 1098.2, 933.6]}, {"text": "the three years in the period ended December 31, 2011.", "bbox": [162.5, 937.7, 624.3, 958.6]}, {"text": "(In millions)", "bbox": [162.5, 1002.3, 250.0, 1019.0]}, {"text": "Consumer", "bbox": [627.4, 985.7, 701.5, 1002.3]}, {"text": "Domestic", "bbox": [631.6, 1002.3, 697.3, 1019.0]}, {"text": "Consumer", "bbox": [732.4, 985.7, 806.5, 1002.3]}, {"text": "International", "bbox": [722.3, 1002.3, 816.7, 1019.0]}, {"text": "SPD", "bbox": [850.2, 1002.3, 881.7, 1019.0]}, {"text": "Corporate(1)", "bbox": [915.5, 1002.3, 1002.2, 1019.0]}, {"text": "As Reported", "bbox": [1023.1, 1002.3, 1112.5, 1019.0]}, {"text": "Net sales", "bbox": [162.5, 1032.4, 240.6, 1053.3]}, {"text": "2011 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 1057.4, 606.6, 1078.5]}, {"text": "$1,979.1", "bbox": [628.0, 1057.4, 700.9, 1078.3]}, {"text": "$509.1", "bbox": [740.8, 1057.4, 798.1, 1078.3]}, {"text": "$261.1", "bbox": [837.4, 1057.4, 894.7, 1078.3]}, {